<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; }
        .info { background: #EEF2FF; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 6px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; padding: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Upcoming Renewal</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{ user.email }},</p>
            
            <p>This is a friendly reminder that your subscription will renew soon.</p>
            
            <div class="info">
                <p><strong>Renewal Date:</strong> {{ subscription.nextBillingDate|date('M d, Y') }}</p>
                <p><strong>Plan:</strong> {{ subscription.plan.name }}</p>
                <p><strong>Amount:</strong> {{ subscription.plan.formattedPrice }}</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Your payment method ending in <strong>{{ subscription.paymentMethodId ? '****' : 'not set' }}</strong> will be charged automatically.</p>
            
            <p><strong>What's included:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                {% for planFeature in subscription.plan.planFeatures|slice(0, 5) %}
                    {% if planFeature.enabled %}
                    <li>{{ planFeature.feature.name }}</li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            
            <p>No action is needed. Your subscription will renew automatically.</p>
            
            <a href="{{ url('subscription_current') }}" class="button">Manage Subscription</a>
            
            <p>If you'd like to change your plan or cancel, you can do so anytime from your subscription dashboard.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} SaaS Starter Pack. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
